# OpenTDCS Licensing

This project uses a multi-license approach to ensure openness while maintaining
appropriate protections for different types of content.

## Hardware Designs — CERN-OHL-S-2.0

**License:** CERN Open Hardware Licence Version 2 - Strongly Reciprocal

**SPDX Identifier:** `CERN-OHL-S-2.0`

**Applies to:**
- Schematics (`docs/schematics.png`)
- 3D models and mechanical designs (`3d/` directory)
- PCB layouts and hardware documentation

**Full text:** See [`LICENSES/CERN-OHL-S-2.0.txt`](LICENSES/CERN-OHL-S-2.0.txt)

## Software and Firmware — GPL-3.0

**License:** GNU General Public License v3.0

**SPDX Identifier:** `GPL-3.0-or-later`

**Applies to:**
- Firmware source code (`firmware/` directory)
- Web GUI application (`gui/` directory)
- Build scripts and tooling

**Full text:** See [`LICENSES/GPL-3.0.txt`](LICENSES/GPL-3.0.txt)

## Documentation — CC-BY-SA-4.0

**License:** Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International

**SPDX Identifier:** `CC-BY-SA-4.0`

**Applies to:**
- README files
- Technical documentation (`TECHNICAL_DETAILS.md`)
- User guides and written content
- Photographs and diagrams (unless otherwise noted)

**Full text:** See [`LICENSES/CC-BY-SA-4.0.txt`](LICENSES/CC-BY-SA-4.0.txt)

